.Dd April 8, 2025
.Dt BITNETCTL 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm bitnetctl
.Nd control tool for bitnetd
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op Fl H Ar host
.Op Fl p Ar port
.Op Fl P Ar pidfile
.Ar command
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
queries and controls a running
.Xr bitnetd 8
instance.
.Pp
The options are as follows:
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Fl H Ar host
Daemon host address.
Default: 127.0.0.1.
.It Fl p Ar port
Daemon port.
Default: 8080.
.It Fl P Ar pidfile
Path to PID file.
Default:
.Pa /var/run/bitnetd.pid .
.El
.Sh COMMANDS
.Bl -tag -width "metrics"
.It Ic status
Show daemon health status.
.It Ic metrics
Show Prometheus metrics.
.It Ic models
List loaded models.
.It Ic reload
Send SIGHUP to reload configuration.
.It Ic stop
Send SIGTERM for graceful shutdown.
.El
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr bitnetd 8 ,
.Xr bitnetd.conf 5
